node.raw_sql:
select
if(sum(credit_entered) != 0, sum(credit_entered), -1) sum_credit, /* if sum is 0, return 1(diff value to debit amount) so that the test fail */
if(sum(debit_entered)  != 0, sum(debit_entered) , -2) sum_debit , /* if sum is 0, return 1(diff value to credit amount) so that the test fail */
sum(credit_entered - debit_entered) diff
from {{ ref('feed_general_ledger') }}
having
    sum_credit != sum_debit OR diff != 0
